       <span class=3D"smalltext">last update: 03 Feb 2004</span><br>
    </td>
    <td>
      This is an old tutorial for flat assembler 1 that has never been fini=
shed. Only the chapter about
      information encoding and some initial sections of the chapter about D=
OS programming are present.
      This document is in PDF format.
    </td>
